com.sterlingcommerce.security.dv.web

Class SCUIJavascriptRuleContainerRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.security.dv.SCDefaultRuleRegistry
      • com.sterlingcommerce.security.dv.web.SCUIJavascriptRuleContainerRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISCRuleRegistry

    public class SCUIJavascriptRuleContainerRegistry
extends SCDefaultRuleRegistry
    This registry implementation is capable of containing javascript validator function along with the ISCValidationRule. The registry takes care of deleting javascript functions if a corresponding rule is deleted. asmishra
